## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or the latest developments in healthcare ethics. Additionally, the information is drawn from secondary sources, which may introduce bias or incomplete data. Further research, including primary sources and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the role of healthcare managers in ethical decision-making.

